data.title: Discovery Horse
data.meta_description: Discovery Horse | 24 followers on LinkedIn. Discovery Horse was born in the high desert of Arizona in 2000. As a Prescott College student, Sara and a fellow classmate, developed Discovery Horse as part of their senior project. Sara went on to graduate and work with other equine organizations, putting Discovery Horse on the back burner to simmer.
